'''傑拉爾德·文森特·布爾'''（'''{{lang-fr|Gerald Vincent Bull}}'''，{{bd|1928年|3月9日|1990年|3月20日|catIdx=Bull, Gerald}}）是一位[[法國|法國]]裔[[加拿大|加拿大]]火砲[[工程師|工程師]]，以幫助[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]政府設計為促進[[經濟|經濟]]而能夠發射[[衛星|衛星]]的超級大砲──《[[巴比倫計畫|巴比倫計畫]]》，而聞名。布爾後來於[[比利時|比利時]][[布魯塞爾|布魯塞爾]]的公寓外被暗殺，推測可能是[[情報特務局|情報特務局]]（俗稱[[摩薩德|摩薩德]]）、[[美國|美國]][[中央情報局|中央情報局]]、[[英國|英國]][[軍情六處|軍情六處]]、[[智利|智利]]或者[[南非|南非]]政府於幕後指使<ref name="NYT1990">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/1990/08/26/magazine/the-man-behind-iraq-s-supergun.html?pagewanted=1|title=The Man Behind Iraq's Supergun|last=Toolis|first=Kevin|date=August 26, 1990|work=New York Times|accessdate=3 April 2010|archive-date=2019-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190115120142/https://www.nytimes.com/1990/08/26/magazine/the-man-behind-iraq-s-supergun.html?pagewanted=1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Harmon|first=Christopher C.|title=Terrorism today|publisher=Routledge|date=2007|pages=43|isbn=9780415773003|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=jAjg-Kc9VcAC&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_v2_summary_r&cad=0#v=onepage&q=&f=false|access-date=2010-09-01|archive-date=2014-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140707153118/http://books.google.com/books?id=jAjg-Kc9VcAC&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_v2_summary_r&cad=0#v=onepage&q=&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=II>{{cite web|title=State assassins who put 007 in the shade|url=http://www.independent.ie/opinion/analysis/state-assassins-who-put-007-inthe-shade-2071971.html|date=February 20, 2010|accessdate=2010-02-20|publisher=Irish Independent|archive-date=2012-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023035720/http://www.independent.ie/opinion/analysis/state-assassins-who-put-007-inthe-shade-2071971.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Are Assassinations Ever Legal? - slate.com">{{cite web|title=Are Assassinations Ever Legal? - slate.com|author=Lapidos, Juliet|publisher=Slate Magazine|url=http://www.slate.com/id/2222843/|accessdate=2009-07-15|date=2009-07-14|archive-date=2011-09-07|a